CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 11, 1953, pg. 10 reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Frederick Dixon wed in Central Baptist Church - Harris Photo. - The wedding of Rosetta Jones, daughter of Mrs. Emily Jones, and Harrison Jones to Frederick Dixon of Washington, D.C., son of Mr. and Mrs. Frederick Dixon of Apollo, Pa., took place in Central Baptist Church on Saturday, June 27, at 7:30 P.M..."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of bride Rosetta Jones Dixon wearing lace gown with lace jacket, and mid length veil, posed holding bouquet in front of plain curtain
